---
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Home">
    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <h1 style="color: #0f172a; font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Chadeau-Hyam Lab</h1>
        <h2 style="color: #0f172a; font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Computational Epidemiology and Biostatistics</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #475569; max-width: 800px;">
            We develop and apply computationally efficient statistical models to integrate high-dimensional multi-omics data, aiming to characterize molecular signatures of the exposome and model complex disease progression.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 2rem;">
        <div>
            <h2 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">Research Focus</h2>
            <p>Our group operates at the critical interface of computational statistics and biology. We leverage massive population biobank data to elucidate rare variant associations and develop novel, computationally robust stability selection methodologies for high-dimensional analysis.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Latest News</h3>
            <ul style="padding-left: 1.2rem; margin: 0; color: #475569;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><strong>Sept 2026:</strong> Short Course (Summer) - London</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>